OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784060308
OL,3,CInquest reveals 'missed opportunities'
OL,4,Cby mental health services after suicide
OL,6,FA Jersey coroner concluded that there
OL,7,Fwere several "missed opportunities" to
OL,8,Fintervene before 25-year-old Daniel
OL,9,FCram took his own life in 2024.
OL,11,FMr Cram was found dead by his sister
OL,12,Fon December 2, 2024, after his mother
OL,13,Fasked her to check on him at their
OL,14,Fhome.
OL,16,FA friend of Mr Cram, Eduardo da Rocha,
OL,17,Ftold ITV News that "he was probably
OL,18,Fthe most genuine person I knew in
OL,19,FJersey".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784060308
OL,3,CInquest reveals 'missed opportunities'
OL,4,Cby mental health services after suicide
OL,6,F"There's not enough words to describe
OL,7,Fsomeone like Daniel", he said.
OL,9,FThe two-day hearing revealed that
OL,10,Fdespite an urgent GP referral that
OL,11,Fdetailed a recent suicide attempt, the
OL,12,FCrisis Assessment Team triaged his
OL,13,Fcase to "routine".
OL,15,FThe inquest, presided over by Deputy
OL,16,FViscount Advocate Matthew Berry, heard
OL,17,Fextensive evidence about the lead-up
OL,18,Fto Mr Cram's death.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784060308
OL,3,CInquest reveals 'missed opportunities'
OL,4,Cby mental health services after suicide
OL,6,FIt emerged that he had sought help
OL,7,Ffrom his GP after a decline in his
OL,8,Fmental health. That had been
OL,9,Fexacerbated by stress at work and a
OL,10,Fperforated eardrum that prevented him
OL,11,Ffrom skateboarding and surfing.
OL,13,FHe sought help from his doctor for the
OL,14,Ffirst time on 22 November. On that
OL,15,Foccasion, he saw Dr Andrew Summers in
OL,16,Fan appointment that lasted "no more
OL,17,Fthan 15 minutes".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784060308
OL,3,CInquest reveals 'missed opportunities'
OL,4,Cby mental health services after suicide
OL,6,FThe doctor told the inquest that he
OL,7,Fhad not been aware of his patient's
OL,8,Fmental health concerns prior to the
OL,9,Fappointment and that he was not told
OL,10,Fabout a recent suicide attempt.
OL,12,FMr Cram was also denied a medical
OL,13,Fcertificate to sign him off work for
OL,14,Fstress reasons. Dr Summers told the
OL,15,Finquest that he did not "did not carry
OL,16,Fout a mental health assessment,
OL,17,Fsuicide risk assessment or consider
OL,18,Freferral to mental health services
OL,19,Fduring that consultation".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784060308
OL,3,CInquest reveals 'missed opportunities'
OL,4,Cby mental health services after suicide
OL,6,FThis was the first missed opportunity
OL,7,Fin Daniel's care that the coroner
OL,8,Fidentified.
OL,10,FThe second came on November 23, 2024
OL,11,Fand involves the intervention of the
OL,12,FCrisis and Assessment Team (CAT).
OL,14,FAnother GP, Dr Ryan saw Mr Cram for a
OL,15,F90-minute assessment alongside his
OL,16,Fmother, during which the patient
OL,17,Fdescribed a recent suicide attempt.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784060308
OL,3,CInquest reveals 'missed opportunities'
OL,4,Cby mental health services after suicide
OL,6,FDuring that time, the doctor then
OL,7,Fplaced an urgent call to Health and
OL,8,FCare Jersey's (HCJ) CAT. A formal
OL,9,Freferral letter was also sent,
OL,10,Frequesting a same-day intervention.
OL,12,FAfter that, the inquest heard that a
OL,13,Flocum mental health practitioner in
OL,14,Fthe CAT triaged the urgent referral as
OL,15,F"routine".
OL,17,FThe CAT decides what category a
OL,18,Fpatient's case falls into, with
OL,19,F"routine" requiring less rapid care
OL,20,Fthan those deemed to be "urgent".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784060308
OL,3,CInquest reveals 'missed opportunities'
OL,4,Cby mental health services after suicide
OL,6,FAfter a brief phone exchange, the CAT
OL,7,Fscheduled an assessment for four days
OL,8,Flater, which Mr Cram subsequently
OL,9,Fmissed.
OL,11,FMr Cram's mother was visibly
OL,12,Ffrustrated during the the inquest. She
OL,13,Ftold GP Dr Ryan "I cannot understand
OL,14,Fhow the brief and superficial
OL,15,Finteraction was enough to downgrade
OL,16,Fthe seriousness of his case".
OL,18,FOne expert witness from the UK,
OL,19,FProfessor Catherine Kinane, agreed
OL,20,Fwith HCJ directors that the triage
OL,21,Fdecision was "not correct".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784060308
OL,3,CInquest reveals 'missed opportunities'
OL,4,Cby mental health services after suicide
OL,6,FIf his case had been treated as
OL,7,F"urgent", Mr Cram would routinely have
OL,8,Fbeen seen within 72 hours and
OL,9,F"possibly even the same day".
OL,11,FThe inquest also found a series of
OL,12,Fcommunication failures, including not
OL,13,Fmaking "assertive attempts" to follow-
OL,14,Fup after the patient missed his follow-
OL,15,Fup CAT appointment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784060308
OL,3,CInquest reveals 'missed opportunities'
OL,4,Cby mental health services after suicide
OL,6,FDr Ryan saw his patient again on
OL,7,FNovember 27 but was not notified about
OL,8,FMr Cram's missed mental health
OL,9,Fappointment. Instead, he assumed that
OL,10,Fhis patient was already engaged with
OL,11,Fmental health services.
OL,13,FBy 1 December, it was eventually
OL,14,Fsuggested that the case be escalated
OL,15,Fto a Multi-Disciplinary Team to
OL,16,Fauthorise a home visit.
OL,18,FIt was then decided that a "cold-call"
OL,19,Fto the patient's home should take
OL,20,Fplace.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784060308
OL,3,CInquest reveals 'missed opportunities'
OL,4,Cby mental health services after suicide
OL,6,FThat was delayed because the MDT team
OL,7,Fdid not operate on weekends at the
OL,8,Ftime. On the day of Mr Cram's death,
OL,9,Fstaff were diverted to other unfolding
OL,10,Fcrises.
OL,12,FAdvocate Berry said that he would
OL,13,Fordinarily issue a formal report to
OL,14,FPrevent Future Deaths.
OL,16,FHe has not done so on this occasion
OL,17,Fbecause Health and Care Jersey say
OL,18,Fthey have already instituted a series
OL,19,Fof reforms after an internal Serious
OL,20,FIncident Investigation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784060308
OL,3,CInquest reveals 'missed opportunities'
OL,4,Cby mental health services after suicide
OL,6,FAndy Weir, the Director of Adult
OL,7,FMental Health Services for Jersey,
OL,8,Ftestified that all seven
OL,9,Frecommendations from the internal
OL,10,Fprobe had been accepted and
OL,11,Fimplemented in March 2025.
OL,13,FUnder new protocols, the CAT now
OL,14,Foperates daily weekend MDT reviews
OL,15,Fwith an on-call psychiatrist. GPs are
OL,16,Fnow also alerted if a vulnerable
OL,17,Fpatient misses a scheduled mental
OL,18,Fhealth appointment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784060308
OL,3,CInquest reveals 'missed opportunities'
OL,4,Cby mental health services after suicide
OL,6,FJersey is also piloting the Mental
OL,7,FHealth Triage Scale. Under that
OL,8,Fsystem, patients with symptoms similar
OL,9,Fto Mr Cram's are mandated to be seen
OL,10,Fwithin 24 hours.
OL,12,FClosing the inquest, Advocate Berry
OL,13,Fexpressed his deep condolences to the
OL,14,FCram family.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
